FBIS3-6988 "dreas056_n_94010" FBIS-EAS-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Mar 1994 Vietnam Ninety-Nine Percent of Spring Crop Complete BK2203075394 Hanoi VNA in English 0622 GMT 22 Mar 94 BK2203075394 Hanoi VNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Hanoi VNA March 22 -- By mid-March, the whole country had cropped 232,260 ha with winter-spring rice, accounting for nearly 99 percent of the plan. In general the paddy is growing well. Meanwhile the southern provinces had harvested 540,140 ha of early winter-spring rice. According to initial reports, the Mekong River delta achieved a yield of 4-6 tons/ha.
